div.p:
Seems certain mob: 
                        (1)

Attacked UB building and burned some
                                UB documents;
                        (2)

Overturned streetcars, etc.;
                        (3)

Invaded jamming station, threw equipment out window and smashed
                            it;
                        (4)

Changed [garble] anti-Soviet and anti-UB slogans;
                        (5)

Carried banners expressing similar sentiments;
                        (6)

Released prisoners from jail;
                        (7)

Tore down Red flags (USSR and Chinese) displayed in connection with
                            the fair; flags then torn into banners with slogans scribbled thereon in
                            school chalk.
